---
// CTA.astro
---

<section class="cta section-pad">
  <div class="cta__bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="cta__bg-grid"></div>
    <div class="cta__bg-glow"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta__inner">
      <p class="label cta__label fade-up" data-i18n="cta.label">Be Part of the Transformation</p>

      <blockquote class="cta__manifesto fade-up">
        <p data-i18n="cta.text1">
          We extend a call to all people to unite our strengths,
          beyond differences of profession, religion, political
          affiliation, sexual orientation, or nationality.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n="cta.text2">
          Together, let us engage in the co-creation of solutions
          to the challenges we share, generate a positive impact on
          our planet, and assume our role as <strong class="accent">
          co-authors of the urgent transformation</strong> our world requires.
        </p>
        <p class="cta__manifesto-strong" data-i18n="cta.text3">
          Because the future is not something we await —
          it is something we build, <em>collectively.</em>
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="cta__actions fade-up">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary" data-i18n="cta.btn1">Join the Movement</a>
        <a href="https://www.wecity.world" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline" data-i18n="cta.btn2">Learn More ↗</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta__bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta__bg-grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(166,224,58,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(166,224,58,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
  }

  .cta__bg-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(166,224,58,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .cta__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta__label { margin-bottom: 2rem; }

  .cta__manifesto {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.35rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(232, 228, 216, 0.8);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .cta__manifesto-strong {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.7rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--col-white);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .cta__actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
</style>